Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim.sdn

Class TimedVm

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.Vm
      • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.sdn.TimedVm
  • public class TimedVm
extends Vm
    Extension of VM that supports to set start and terminate time of VM in VM creation request. If start time and finish time is set up, specific CloudSim Event is triggered in datacenter to create and terminate the VM.
    Since:
    CloudSimSDN 1.0
    Author:
    Jungmin Son, Rodrigo N. Calheiros
